## Limitations
This report is based on a limited number of sources and may not capture all possible challenges related to diversity and inclusion in the workplace. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of workplace dynamics means that new challenges may emerge that are not covered in this report. Further research and continuous monitoring of the field are recommended to stay updated on the latest trends and issues.